# PlayPlay (Spotify property — kept out of the public repository).
# Wavee follows strict guidelines (proper user-agents, playback events, no
# abuse). Tracks are chunked per user request and not stored to disk.
# PlayPlay keys are only cached in obfuscated form and still require the same
# algorithm to read. The stubs alongside (PlayPlayConstants.Stub.cs,
# PlayPlayKeyEmulator.Stub.cs, Program.Stub.cs) keep the build green; the
# runtime feature stays disabled when the real files are absent.
Wavee/Core/Audio/PlayPlayConstants.cs
Wavee.AudioHost/PlayPlay/PlayPlayKeyEmulator.cs
Wavee.PlayPlay.Tests/Program.cs

# Local Spotify.dll copies (binary belongs to Spotify; verified at runtime
# against a SHA-256 baked into PlayPlayConstants).
**/Spotify.dll

# Out-of-tree dev tooling and per-user state — kept local, not in source control.
# - worker/: Cloudflare Worker for feedback-proxy (separate deploy lifecycle)
# - scripts/: Local diagnostic / WPA-profiling scripts
# - docs/superpowers/specs/: superpowers-skill working specs
# - .dotnet-cli/: project-scoped dotnet SDK install (per-machine path)
# - .claude/: Claude Code per-user settings + memory
worker/
scripts/
docs/superpowers/specs/
.dotnet-cli/
.claude/

# Signing — local Artifact Signing config and any code-signing certificates.
# metadata.json carries the developer's Azure account/profile names; *.pfx
# and *.cer are private/public keys for self-signed dev certs. Never commit.
signing/metadata.json
*.pfx
*.cer

# Local signed-MSIX output staging — large per-build artifacts (100MB+).
.signed-msix/

# Protocol-capture binaries / Spotify reverse-engineering scratch.
# Anything in bodies/ is research material, not source.
bodies/

# Superpowers planning files: working notes the workflow generates and
# discards each session. Already gitignored under docs/superpowers/specs/;
# include the broader subtree so /loop and /plan output never leaks.
docs/superpowers/

# Various AI-tool sandbox/cache directories created at the repo root by
# host-side coding agents. None of these are source.
.codex-ai-compile/
.codex-dotnet-home/
.codex-dumps/
.codex-har-inspect/
.dotnet-cli-home/
.dotnet-home/
